column2: SELECT m.recno, m.ra AS ra1, m.dec AS dec1, n.objid, n.distance, sp.ra AS ra_sdss, sp.dec AS dec_sdss, sp.mode, sp.fiberMag_u, sp.fiberMagErr_u, sp.fiberMag_g, sp.fiberMagErr_g, sp.fiberMag_r, sp.fiberMagErr_r, sp.fiberMag_i, sp.fiberMagErr_i, sp.fiberMag_z, sp.fiberMagErr_z, sp.z , sp.zErr , sp.zWarning, sp.class , sp.subClass into mydb.SyCATv1#comsdssdr1# from MyDB.SyCATv1# AS m CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq (m.ra, m.dec, #) AS n JOIN SpecPhotoAll AS sp ON n.objid = sp.objid
